AddressInfo.Title: YASNO E-Mobility / 50 kW (Promenada Park)
AddressInfo.AccessComments: 24h access. The charger is located on the right (north) side of the 'Promenada Park' shopping mall. At the entrance to the area of mall, aturn to the right, and after a few meters to the left. Parking is free.

GeneralComments:
Registration, top-up & charging via 'STRUM Charging' mobile app (iOS/Android), at least 25.00 kWh must be available on the account at the start of each charging session. Parking is free. You can book your STRUM card only after registrartion & top-up by sending request to support.strum@dtek.com.

You pay only for kWh, no fees for time or session. Price during top-up is 9 UAH/KWH (≈ 0.3 €/KWH). While charging on CHAdeMO/CCS, 1 KWH is taken away for each 1 kWh of charging. While charging on Type2, 0.5 KWH is taken away for each 1 kWh of charging (half price). Actual prices at http://strum.dtek.com/en/prices/.

Android App download - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.beenergised.chargemobile.dtek&hl=en
iOS App download - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/strum-charging/id1368596475?mt=8
